Standard R cars data set

Source: R/data.R
chk.Rd

This is the standard mtcars data set included with base R.

Usage

chk

Format

'chk'

A data frame with 32 rows and 11 variables:

mpg

miles per gallon

cyl

number of cylinders

disp

engine displacement

hp

engine horse power

drat

drag racing power

wt

weight of car

qsec

quality per second

vs

vital sign of car

am

type of radio

gear

number of gears

carb

number of carburetors
